<FILE_CONTENT name="README.md" target-output-path="./react-bun-example/README.md">
```md
# React Bun Example

A basic React app using Bun, Vite, TypeScript, and Tailwind CSS.

## Run

```bash
bun install
bun run dev
```

## Build

```bash
bun run build
```
```
</FILE_CONTENT>
